with a massive contents, a new code
and layout and of course 4 modules to
enjoy a nice afternoon of reading the
latest in »CL1:Amiga Scene new&stories»..
There is still time to send your
support and convince Soda to be a
little bit more active at
»CL1:RETRO@SOFTHOME.NET»

